owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pairAssetConvertible().details: The withdrawal mechanism is ZVE/pairAsset_LP => pairAsset.

params.ids: The IDs of the assets within the ERC1155 to migrate.

params.tokenId: The ID of the NFT to migrate.

params.tokenIds: The IDs of the NFTs to migrate.

params.amounts: The amounts of "assets" to migrate, corresponds to "assets" by position in array.

params.tokenId: The ID of the NFT to migrate.

params.amounts: The amount to pull of each asset respectively.
params.assets: The assets to pull from the DAO.

params.tokenIds: The IDs of the NFTs to migrate.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

transferOwnershipAndLock(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

updateCompoundingRateBIPS(uint256).details: A value of 2,000 represent 20% of the earnings stays in this contract, compounding.

canPull().notice: Permission for owner to call pullFromLocker().

canPullPartial().notice: Permission for owner to call pullFromLockerPartial().

canPushMulti().notice: Permission for owner to call pushToLockerMulti().

forwardYield().notice: This forwards yield to the YDL in the form of pairAsset.

forwardYieldKeeper(bytes).notice: This function converts and forwards available "amountForConversion" to YDL.distributeAsset().

pairAssetConvertible().notice: Returns information on how much pairAsset is convertible via current LP tokens.

pullFromLocker(address).notice: This burns LP tokens from the $ZVE/pairAsset pool and returns them to the DAO.

pullFromLockerERC1155(address,uint256[],.notice: Migrates ERC1155 assets from locker to owner().

pullFromLockerERC721(address,uint256,byt.notice: Migrates an ERC721 from locker to owner().

pullFromLockerMulti(address[]).notice: Migrates full amount of ERC20s from locker to owner().

pullFromLockerMultiERC721(address[],uint.notice: Migrates ERC721s from locker to owner().

pullFromLockerMultiPartial(address[],uin.notice: Migrates specific amounts of ERC20s from locker to owner().

pullFromLockerPartial(address,uint256).notice: This burns LP tokens from the $ZVE/pairAsset pool and returns them to the DAO.

pushToLocker(address,uint256).notice: Migrates specific amount of ERC20 from owner() to locker.

pushToLockerERC1155(address,uint256[],ui.notice: Migrates ERC1155 assets from owner() to locker.

pushToLockerERC721(address,uint256,bytes.notice: Migrates an ERC721 from owner() to locker.

pushToLockerMulti(address[],uint256[]).notice: This pulls capital from the DAO and adds liquidity into a $ZVE/pairAsset pool.

pushToLockerMultiERC721(address[],uint25.notice: Migrates ERC721s from owner() to locker.

updateCompoundingRateBIPS(uint256).notice: Updates the compounding rate of this contract.
